'''FaunOS''' is a portable, fully integrated [[operating system]] based on [[Arch Linux]], which can run from a USB Flash Drive or a DVD. As of 20 September 2008, the project has been [http://bbs.archlinux.org/viewtopic.php?id=55524 discontinued].

A [[Live USB]] of FaunOS can be created manually or with [[UNetbootin]] <ref>[http://unetbootin.sourceforge.net/]</ref>.

